Smuxi is in the official [FreeBSD ports tree][], so just run the
following comand to install it from ports:

    make -C /usr/ports/irc/smuxi/ install clean

Use this alternative to install it quickly using binary packages

    pkg install smuxi
    
Now you can start Smuxi from the GNOME or KDE menu.

  [FreeBSD ports tree]: http://www.freshports.org/irc/smuxi/
